      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). It indicates the deep anxiety of Epaphras for this beloved and endangered Church. There is nothing here to point to \"outward toil\" (Lightfoot), any more than in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Colossians 2:1",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The apostle loves to commend his fellow labourers (",
